        <samplingProcedure xml:lang="en">Industry data, representative 100 % of European (EU-28) production capacity, based on production volumes in 2018.

The industrial data used originate from three different TDI producers, with three plant, in two different European countries.
</samplingProcedure>
        <extrapolations xml:lang="en">This dataset has been copied from an original dataset covering the geography RER. The uncertainty has been adjusted accordingly.

The catalyst and stabilizer use, with a representation on dry mass input lower than 0.01%, was cut-off. Furthermore, an exchange representing unreacted raw materials that are recycled to the process after treatment, with a representation of 3.3% on dry mass output, was cut-off.

</extrapolations>
